      "number": 5,
      "id": "I_kwDOMjLqms6dDX1r",
      "title": "Make an exception for mobile networks",
      "url": "https://github.com/buraglio/draft-nbtjjl-dnsop-prefer8781/issues/5",
      "state": "OPEN",
      "author": "furry13",
      "authorAssociation": "COLLABORATOR",
      "assignees": [
        "furry13"
      ],
      "labels": [],
      "body": "",
      "createdAt": "2024-11-05T09:30:01Z",
      "updatedAt": "2024-11-19T15:59:08Z",
      "closedAt": null,
      "comments": [
        {
          "author": "buraglio",
          "authorAssociation": "OWNER",
          "body": "I think we should not exempt mobile carriers. 7050 may need to exist for a long time even in enterprise cases, but we should make clear that the preferred method is 8781. ",
          "createdAt": "2024-11-11T21:21:41Z",
          "updatedAt": "2024-11-11T21:21:41Z"
        },
        {
          "author": "furry13",
          "authorAssociation": "COLLABORATOR",
          "body": "Apparently those networks do not use RAs to configure clients. So we can say that the recommendations in the draft do not apply to the networks which do not use SLAAC for client config.\r\n\r\nLong-term solution might be going to 3GPP ;)",
          "createdAt": "2024-11-19T15:59:06Z",
          "updatedAt": "2024-11-19T15:59:06Z"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "number": 6,
      "id": "I_kwDOMjLqms6dF4hi",
      "title": "New terminology to replace \"deprecation\" term",
      "url": "https://github.com/buraglio/draft-nbtjjl-dnsop-prefer8781/issues/6",
      "state": "CLOSED",
      "author": "buraglio",
      "authorAssociation": "OWNER",
      "assignees": [],
      "labels": [],
      "body": "There are some requirements tied to the term \"deprecation\" that we may want to avoid. Perhaps a new title such as \"Encourage use of pref64 over RFC7050/DNS64/DNS for IPv6-only prefix discovery\" may assuage the formality. ",
      "createdAt": "2024-11-05T14:05:54Z",
      "updatedAt": "2024-11-11T21:23:32Z",
      "closedAt": "2024-11-11T21:23:32Z",
      "comments": [
        {
          "author": "buraglio",
          "authorAssociation": "OWNER",
          "body": "changed to \"Preference of pref64 over DNS64 for Discovery of IPv6 Prefix Used for IPv6 Address Synthesis\"",
          "createdAt": "2024-11-11T21:23:25Z",
          "updatedAt": "2024-11-11T21:23:25Z"
        }
      ]
